      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-500 mb-4">🍲 Dapur Koemau</h3>
        <p class="text-orange-500">Nikmati cita rasa autentik makanan tradisional kami dengan bahan berkualitas tinggi dan resep yang telah teruji.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Quick Links</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-500 transition">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-500 transition">About Us</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-500 transition">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="/location" class="text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-500 transition">Location</a></li>
        </ul>
